ccusage
-------

BlockWatcher vendors ccusage as a git submodule at commit
7acee6c5853c26fe66fbe1453bd94c9376afec06 and builds it as an offline Tauri
sidecar. The Claude session-block computation in core/src/blocks.rs is also
ported from ccusage.

Source: https://github.com/ccusage/ccusage
Copyright (c) 2025 ryoppippi
License: MIT

